Class 5

Handling Checkboxes and RadioButtons:
1. if you have only one checkbox or radiobutton -- you can simply click on it
2. if you have multiple checkboxes or radiobuttons - store them in a list and loop through

Dropdowns
Dropdown is a menu which allows you to select one or multiple options

Types of Dropdowns:
1. Single select
2. Multiple Select

Handling DropDowns:
1. click on the dropdown click on the option
2. using Select Class:
                in order to use select class we need to make sure we have
                a <select> tag in html

Selecting options from dropdown can be done in 3 ways:
1. by index
2. by visible text
3. by value

In order to deselect options from dropdown we can use the following methods:
Your DD must be multiple select
deselectByIndex()
deselectByVisibleText()
deselectByValue()
deselectAll()


